  tokens of bar","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This provider should be integrated as a ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllBarComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"BarComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"bar"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Bar","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of colors ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProviders"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"), borders (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":